BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:SS4gjSqdCHZ9kLs-mJmix
SUMMARY:Gate City IPA Trivia Night
DTSTAMP:20260308T063051Z
DTSTART:20250514T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for this Seattle Beer Week 16 event! Two rounds of triv
	ia at 7pm and 8pm and delicious hazy IPA for a great cause. Free to play. 
	CALL AHEAD TO RESERVE YOUR SPOT - 206.729.7433With every pint and pitcher 
	sold\, a donation is made to North Helpline\, helping to keep food on the 
	table and a roof overhead for our neighbors. Drinking a great IPA counts a
	s a good deed for the day!About Gate City Community Benefit:Hellbent Brewi
	ng\, Watershed Pub &amp\; Kitchen\, Project 9 Brewing\, and local communit
	y partners have come together again to organize the 8th annual Seattle Bee
	r Week event that features Hellbent Brewing’s award-winning Gate City IPA.
	 A combination of the two Seattle neighborhoods\, Northgate and Lake City\
	, this brew celebrates the North Seattle community by raising funds for No
	rth Helpline.Meet with North Helpline staff\, win fun prizes\, and enjoy G
	ate City IPA throughout Seattle Beer Week! Stay tuned for more details.\n\
	nFrom Seattle Beer Week
LOCATION:Location ID: m992z2fo
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:beer-week
CATEGORIES:Seattle Beer Week
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
